WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:04.500
It is easy to cite or download a text from the Werkstatt.

00:04.700 --> 00:07.200
To see our suggested citation form,

00:07.200 --> 00:11.500
simply click on the quotations marks under the text's title.

00:12.000 --> 00:14.000
You can then copy the citation

00:14.000 --> 00:16.500
from the tooltip window.

00:17.500 --> 00:20.000
To download a PDF of the text,

00:20.000 --> 00:23.000
click on the document download symbol

00:23.000 --> 00:24.500
under the text's title.

00:25.000 --> 00:29.500
You can then save the resulting PDF to your computer.

00:30.000 --> 00:34.500
On this PDF you will find the suggested citation form

00:35.000 --> 00:38.000
at the bottom of each page.
